Commment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:56.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}センセーションを巻き起こしちゃう恋愛観のベクトルへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:03.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}一直線で向かってくんだ、ついて来れるかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}たとえば目と目 (合ったりした瞬間)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:18.61,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}ひょっとして…なんて期待?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:22.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}教室はまるで (アッチとコッチ飛び交う)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:25.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}視線のハイウェイ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:29.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}見えないはずの (確証的相互理解)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:33.06,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}瞳になぜか映って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:36.65,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}ジャンクションのなかで (確信的ナビゲーション)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:40.60,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}迷わないで行くよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:47.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}すれ違えない…こんなに近くちゃ、ぶつかっちゃうよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:55.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}一方通行じゃヤダ! CROSS × OVER?それでいいよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:03:03.21,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}センセーショナルなインパクトに乗って恋愛キブン重なれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:10.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}一直線で向かっていくんだ、スピードを上げて!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:17.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}CROSS × OVER したココロぶつかって、恋を巻き起こす!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:56.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}掀起情感的热潮  走上恋爱轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:03.81,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}笔直地向前奔跑  你可跟得上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}眼神与眼神  (相交的瞬间)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:18.61,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}莫非在期待着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:22.19,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}教室就好像  (纵横交错的)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:25.51,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}视线的高速公路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:29.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}本应无法看到  (坚定的相互理解)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:33.06,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}却在你眼中倒映
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:36.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}在交叉点之上  (正确的导航)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:40.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}别犹豫向前冲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:47.80,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}无法擦身而过  如此接近  马上就要迸出火花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:55.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}从此拒绝单行道  愿与你心灵交汇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:03:03.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}顺着强烈的感觉  乘着恋爱的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:10.28,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}笔直地向前奔跑  加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:17.45,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\bord2.5}触碰彼此相交的心  掀起恋爱热潮
Commment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱动  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就不好弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  香织理  这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心交给我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为什么要在我的房间里换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为  如果我和千早单独在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人会产生奇怪的误解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来行了  要用听诊器时你就解开一个纽扣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来健康检查就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你不好意思在人前裸露就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像千早这样的名人要是鬼鬼祟祟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而会更引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的眼光来看千早如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圣应女学院里拥有盛名的银公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是粗鲁的男性？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很让人不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…应该说  漂亮得让人连不甘心的心情都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位姐姐  需要来一点甜食吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史最喜欢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夹心冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过谁吃得下这么多啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小史最喜欢的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  多吃一些  小史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  坐下坐下  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Commment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是顺利做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就能暂时安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安  银公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士君  贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚转学过来就能被冠上称号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是千早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子才是  我觉得这称号威风凛凛正适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  千早你其实很爱逗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子其实很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就会捉弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  千早你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅乐乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫哘雅乐乃  是合奏团中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了敬爱的千早姐姐  一定专心致志去做好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是同为合奏团的仁科卫里  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  看样子我才是该求教的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想给千早姐姐说明一下这次的演奏会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  淡雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  为什么华道部部长的小雅乐要干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能帮得上姐姐的忙我都乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  关于演奏会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为圣应女学院的学生  应当喜好音律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每年都有一次由音乐成绩优秀的人组成合奏团开演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  今年的观赏座号票的争夺战似乎已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生的演奏会居然还有座号票？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都会被美丽的事物所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  你太不端庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子姐姐看来非常烦恼演奏会的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏会的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  薰子担当的是什么乐器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年是大提琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  大提琴是兼具优美与豁达的乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟薰子是完美搭配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  去年的薰子那演奏可是相当厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初音  你这肯定不是在夸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是那种音乐可不是随便能演奏出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个讲堂都冻结了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是在夸我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长在那么多人面前演奏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的演奏  我想听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连优雨也这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子的大提琴  我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  千早姐姐擅长什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴的话略懂一二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  弹给我们听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请演奏一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就献丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  弹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早你真是无所不能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  我到处都是缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯莉就是首席演奏者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是二年级生君原春美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3岁开始就练习小提琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以首席演奏者就交给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识您  骑士君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  柔和地  非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位就像雷诺阿的画一般优美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为千早姐姐粉丝俱乐部会员能在这里真是幸福至极
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏千早教导  总算是有模有样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事  全是因为薰子的专心和努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好像是在催促我拼命努力一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这次让我们大家一起合奏试试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们也已经预约好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  卫里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于音乐室的使用许可发生了一些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这是实行委员会的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双重预约了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又无法同时练习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要决定两者之一来使用音乐室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都是弦乐器来编成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起要用钢琴的千早移动更方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能这么说那真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这与编成无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得条件是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯  对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君原同学说的也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好宿舍里有直立式钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够满足我的个人练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的练习就让我们在宿舍里进行如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子也同意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫里也同意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这件事就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位没有问题了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:11:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:37.98,title0,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}身为少女的苦恼与旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  昨天见到的那位君原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听她同班的人说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏会结束后她就要转学了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时期有点奇怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一般转学都是在学期开始前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是她家里发生了什么变故
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信贷公司？借钱的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是家相当蛮横的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪看起来这么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  她会听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道会被她如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君原春美同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找找薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气看起来也不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家中的变故是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  正如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的公司资金周转不灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给薰子姐姐的父亲也添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  有需要我帮忙的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧  只要我力所能及什么事都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我想错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为薰子姐姐和我在这里的立场是对等的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士君果然还是不折不扣的千金小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说什么事都愿意做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为薰子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子姐姐你不是拥有一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把那些东西都给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友  人望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有在圣应的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那位是君原同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气预报说这将是持续整晚的大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子姐姐刚刚出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种天气里出门？她去哪里了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉  我向她打招呼但她似乎没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去附近找一找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信贷公司？借钱的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是家相当蛮横的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  她会听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道会被她如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子姐姐你不是拥有一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把那些东西都给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君原同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你都受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得必须抓紧时间练习…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和君原同学  是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮不上忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我是男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我当初欺骗过薰子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出口  你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我  薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…一定会讨厌我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早听了后肯定也会讨厌我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对哭着寻求帮助的她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样  得过且过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然总想着下次要做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还是无法面对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:19:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我好不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子真善良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此专心  如此拼命  如此纯真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我  依靠片刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…一直很反感自己是出生在借贷公司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讨厌这样反感的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  却没有直视的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮不了任何人的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想君原同学也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是薰子的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那是出自薰子的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不一定是正确的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们只能祈求君原同学能坚强地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  希望她能加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气  连这一份善良在内…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我心目中最美的薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  紧张死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子姐姐看起来不太紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说也许是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想过替你承担一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我  你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是必须承认的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  我想一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却无法实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我应该对你怀恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却无法抛弃对你的仰慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨就恨吧  仰慕就仰慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  我是绝对不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:22:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…果然薰子姐姐就是骑士君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:39.14,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(1000,1000)}身为少女的苦恼与旋律
